data.description: Beautiful custom home situated in the desirable Lake Wellington Estates neighborhood and walking distance to West foundation Elementary school. Recently remodeled kitchen with granite and stainless steel appliances. All bathrooms updated with granite and new fixtures. Spacious 2348 ft.² with abundant storage, large dining room, two living areas, gas fireplace and large breakfast area in kitchen. Bedroom one and two are good sized and have a full bath nearby. Bedroom three is isolated loft bedroom upstairs with its own bathroom and shower. Bedroom four is an oversized master suite with an exit to a beautiful cedar covered outside patio. The master bathroom has a large, almost 9 foot walk-in shower with rainfall and handheld showers and large walk-in closet.  Must see to appreciate all this house has the offer! Call now 940-704-5511. Offering 3% buyers agent commission.
data.whatILove: Beautiful home in a quiet neighborhood close to town and within walking distance to West Foundation elementary school. Plenty of storage and a beautiful covered patio to enjoy your time outside. Four spacious bedrooms and three bathrooms—room for the whole family!
